$ PowerShell: the automatic variable $sender

The → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic[automatic variable] `$sender` corresponds to the object that generated an event.

`$sender` is the same object as found with `(get-event).sender`.

sa:

  → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/objectEvent/register[`register-objectEvent`].

  Other → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic[automatic variables] such as
    → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/event[`$event`],
    → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/eventSubscriber[`$eventSubscriber`] and
    → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/eventArgs[`$eventArgs`].
